K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:433b-1: a'arya dr'a bi da bidya r'a dza /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434a-1: phyogs na rgyun gyi bdag po zhes bya ba'i glog yod de /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434a-3: gang la la glog 'di rnams kyi ming shes pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-0: pim ga @434b l'akshi da dhi mu khi /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-4: de nas gsang ba pa'i bdag po lag na rdo rjes bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de logs su thal mo sbyar ba btud de bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-6: bdag gis kyang chos kyi rnam grangs 'di la gzungs kyi tshig rnams brjod par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-7: tadya th'a; mu ni mu ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-14: khyod la sdig pa med kyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-15: ma 'jigs shig ces lag na rdo rjes smras kyi /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-18: bdag gi srung ba gzhan gyis mi thub pa 'di su'i snying la 'dzin tam /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-20: de la bdag gis rtag par rgyun du 'jigs pa thams cad las bsrung bar bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-21: dus ma lags par 'gum pa thams cad las thar par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-22: de nas mi mjed kyi bdag po tshangs pas bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:434b-24: bdag gis kyang sems can thams cad kyi don dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435a-5: brahma sva re sva re sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435a-6: brahma garbha pushpa sam sta re sv'ah'a /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435a-11: sdig pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar bgyid pa lags so //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435a-14: bdag gis kyang chos kyi rnam grangs 'di la gzungs kyi gsang sngags kyi gzhi rnams brjod par bgyi'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435a-26: hi na ma dhya ma dh'a ra n'i ma la ni /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-2: bcom ldan 'das; bdag gis kyang skye bo mang po la sman pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-15: rgyal po chen po bzhi po bdag cag gi srung ba 'jigs pa ma mchis pa zhes bya ste /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-16: 'jigs pa thams cad la mi 'jigs par bgyid pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-18: dus ma lags par 'gum pa thams cad las yongs su skyob pa lags so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-19: de nas klu'i rgyal po rgya mtsho dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-23: klu'i rgyal po 'od zer brgya pas bcom ldan 'das ga la ba de logs su thal mo sbyar ba btud de bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-25: bdag cag gi srung ba chen po yid bzhin gyi nor bu zhes bgyi ba glog thams cad zlog pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:435b-26: dus ma lags par 'gum pa thams cad sel ba /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-1: rnams mi gdug par bgyid pa /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-5: bkra mi shis pa 'jigs par bgyid pa mchis na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-7: bdag cag klu'i skye gnas 'di nas dbyung ba dang /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-8: ser sna spang ba'i slad du thugs brtse bar dgongs te bzhes su gsol /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-9: de ci'i slad du zhe na /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-10: bcom ldan 'das; bdag cag klu rnams ni /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-12: sems ser snas kun nas dkris pa lags pa'i slad du'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-17: aaksha ye; pu n+ya parya ba te /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-18: sarba p'a pa pra sha ma n'a ya sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-19: aarya pu n+ya so pa k'i ye sv'ah'a /
K12acip-k_lha_sa-090-078:436a-21: gsang sngags kyi gzhi 'di dag skyes pa'am /
